<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000247-B046-192</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://tourism.tourism.gov.au:80/publications/BPE/EnergySupply.html 192.199.45.253 19970108084739 text/html 9808
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: CERN/3.0
