<DOCNO>WT06-B34-6</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000247-B046-225</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://tourism.tourism.gov.au:80/publications/BPE/RecoveringHeat.html 192.199.45.253 19970108084844 text/html 3163
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
