<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000247-B046-321</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://tourism.tourism.gov.au:80/publications/BPE/BuildingMaterials.html 192.199.45.253 19970108085104 text/html 5600
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
