<DOCNO>WT06-B34-21</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA023-000247-B046-353</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://tourism.tourism.gov.au:80/publications/BPE/MetalContainers.html 192.199.45.253 19970108085146 text/html 5006
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: CERN/3.0
