<P ALIGN="LEFT">The Energy Programs and Fisheries Division of the 
Commonwealth Department of Primary 
Industries and Energy focuses on programs to promote innovative energy 
supply by 
increasing the use of new efficient renewable and non-renewable energy 
technologies.
<P ALIGN="LEFT">The Department can provide useful information on energy 
efficiency through various 
publications, including industry advisory booklets and energy technology 
discussion 
papers.
<P ALIGN="LEFT">For further information, contact:<P>


