<P ALIGN="LEFT">The New South Wales Office of Energy produces and 
maintains publications with information 
and statistics on various aspects of energy and energy use. Among them is 
<CITE>Energy Focus,</CITE>
 a bimonthly publication containing interesting and informative articles 
on energy 
