Program</B></FONT>

<P ALIGN="LEFT">The Cleaner Production Grants Program assists Victorian 
industry to reduce the amount 
and level of hazardous waste generated. It promotes clean technology and 
encourages 
small and medium firms to invest in low waste, no waste or clean 
technologies to 
reduce pollution and conserve resources.
<P ALIGN="LEFT">For further information, contact:<P>


