<HR SIZE=4 WIDTH=75% ALIGN=CENTER><P>
<P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT SIZE=4><B>South Australian Tourism 
Commission</B></FONT>

<P ALIGN="LEFT">The South Australian Tourism Commission has published a 
series of guidelines for ecotourism 
operations. The report, <CITE>Ecotourism: A South Australian Design Guide 
for Sustainable Development </CITE>
covers all ecotourism-related issues including site selection, 
development, management 
and operation and includes a checklist for those undertaking an 
ecotourism development.
