<DOCHDR>
http://tourism.tourism.gov.au:80/publications/forecast/April95/VisitorArrivals.html 192.199.45.253 19970108085331 text/html 23034
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: CERN/3.0
