Victoria, Melbourne.</P><P>Western Australia Tourism Commission 1994,
<I>Getting into Host Tourism, B&amp;B's, Farms Stay, Guest Houses,
Station Stay, </I>WATC, Perth.</P><P></P><P>Western Australia Tourism
Commission and Farm Country Holidays Association Inc. 1994, <I>Farm,
Station &amp; Country Retreats Holidays in Western Australia,
</I>ART Publishing, Perth.</P><P></P><P>Western Australia Tourism
Commission, Nature Based Tourism Advisory Committee 1994, <I>Towards a
Nature Based Tourism Strategy for Western Australia Discussion Paper
August 1994, </I>WATC, Perth.</P><P></P></BODY></HTML>
</DOC>
