<TITLE> Crisscross 20,000 Unlimited Access</TITLE>
<BODY bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC=Unlimited.gif>
<IMG SRC=UnlimitedE.gif>


<P><FONT SIZE=4>Access the internet as often and for as long as you like for only 20,000yen per year. 
<BR>There are <B>no extra time charges</B>. No monthly fees.<BR>
<P>Just one payment takes care of your entire internet access for the year.
<P>Unlimited Access accounts include your own e-mail address 
<BR>(yourname@crisscross.com) and 10MB space for your own <A HREF=UsersHomePages.html>home pages.</A>

<P>There is one-time set-up fee of 10,000Yen for this service.<P>
<HR>


