</TABLE>

</center>


<p>
<hr size=2></p>

<p></p>



<font size=+2>And if you're still interested... follow <blink><a href="Jesse"> Commander Jesse's</a></blink> path to becoming
 the Power Ranger he is today!

<p><b><i><font SIZE=+0>For some reason, this stupid picture
has been the most confusing part of my page for most.  This is just a joke picture of me with one of my friends (Eitan).  I look bad
and he looks worse:<a href="http://www.crisscross.com/users/aleaxndr/home1">  A
Picture of my Girl</a>
<p>
Many people have been asking me why I have a vampire page.  Well here is an<a href="http://www.crisscross.com/users/aleaxndr/Expo">
explaination</a></font></i></b> of sorts.</p>

