<HTML><BODY BACKGROUND="Images/Tile01.jpg" TEXT="000000" LINK="0000ff" ALINK="ff0000" VLINK="c000c0"><H2><center>Company Profiles & P.R.</H2><P><B><font size="+1"><a href="InfoPage">Eduardo Galvani - Art Director</B></P></a></font><P><B>ABOUT THE IMAGES</B></P><P>You see here samples of Annual Reports, Company Profiles and general P.R. Material. Some photos are supplied by the client and used as it is. Others images are done by me, as covers, illustrations and computer graphics.</P><P>For traditional images, the picture is first scanned and then processed on Photoshop or other image editing soft. The desktop publishing is QuarkXpress. 2-D illustrations are done with Adobe Illustrator and Freehand. The film is done with digital-printing technology.</P><P><B>Click on the preview icon for to see a enlarged version of the art.</B></P><P><EM>All images are copyrighted. Please, do not reproduce or distribute the images without consent.</EM><B>. </B></P><HR><P><B>Company Profile: Singapore Airlines</B></P><P><A HREF=Images/D01.jpg><IMG SRC=Images/D01S.jpg></A> </P><HR><P><B>Company Profile: Singapore Airlines</B></P><P><A HREF=Images/D02.jpg><IMG SRC=Images/D02S.jpg></A> </P><HR><P><B>Company Profile: Canon Inc.</B></P><P><A HREF=Images/D03.jpg><IMG SRC=Images/D03S.jpg></A> </P><HR><P><B>Company Profile: ThreeBond Inc.</B></P><P><A HREF=Images/D04.jpg><IMG SRC=Images/D04S.jpg></A> </P><HR><P><B>Annual Report: The Fukuoka City Bank</B></P><P><A HREF=Images/D05.jpg><IMG SRC=Images/D05S.jpg></A> </P><HR><P><B>Annual Report: The Fukuoka City Bank</B></P><P><A HREF=Images/D06.jpg><IMG SRC=Images/D06S.jpg></A> </P><HR><P><B>Annual Report: Sanyo Securities Co.Ltd.</B></P><P><A HREF=Images/D07.jpg><IMG SRC=Images/D07S.jpg></A> </P><HR><P><B>Annual Report: Sanyo Securities Co.Ltd.</B></P><P><A HREF=Images/D08.jpg><IMG SRC=Images/D08S.jpg></A> </P><HR><P><B>Annual Report: Daiei OMC</B></P><P><A HREF=Images/D09.jpg><