<HTML><BODY BACKGROUND="Images/Logo.jpg" TEXT="000000" LINK="0000ff" ALINK="ff0000" VLINK="c000c0"><IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC=Images/Io.gif><P><CITE><B><font size="+3">Information</B></font></CITE></P><P><B><font size="+1"><a href="mailto:paradox@crisscross.com">Eduardo Galvani - Art Director</B></P></a></font></P><P><B><CITE>About me</CITE></B></P><P><B>For the last seven years I had been living in Japan, working as a freelance Art Director. As you can see from my samples, my design is not limited to a specific field, it ranges from advertising, traditional & computer illustration, package & industrial design, graphic design, to web-site design as this virtual-portfolio. Even having Japan as my primary market I do work for Europe and United States clients as well. </B></P><P><B>Some of my clients:</B>Canon Inc., Ricoh Inc., Casio Computers, Sanyo Securities, Chiyoda-Life Securities, Dai-Ichi Optec, Toshigi Bank, Seibu Bank, Fukuoka City Bank, Mitsubishi Inc., Daiei-Omc Financial, Krizia Fashion, Nara Camice- Japan, Zenrin, Solleone Group, Tokyo City Government, Far East Travelers Reports, Tokyo Classifieds and others.</P><CENTER><P><B>Fax from out-side Japan: (Your international access code) + 81-429-47-2046</P><P>Fax from Japan: 0429-47-2046</B></P></CENTER><IMG ALIGN=RIGHT SRC=Images/Walk.gif><HR><P></P><CENTER><A HREF=Page1.html>Illustration & CG /</A><A HREF=Page2.html>AD & Promotion /</A><A HREF=Page3.html>Pack & Industrial design /</A><A HREF=Page4.html>Company Profile & PR /</A><A HREF=Home.html><BLINK>Home Page</BLINK></A><P></P><b><P>For more information & comments, please Email me at <a href="mailto:paradox@crisscross.com">paradox@crisscross.com.</a></P></b></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
