nd orders to restrict resuscitation. Hospital and      Community Psychiatry 1991;42:189-91.<P>28. Michaelson C, Mulvihill M, Hsu MA, et al. Eliciting medical care preferences  from        nursing home residents. Gerontologist 1991;31:358-63.<P>29. Doi T. The Anatomy of Dependence. Tokyo: Kodansha International, 1973.<P>30. Berger D, Ono Y, Kumano H, et al. The Japanese concept of      interdependency. (Letter) American Journal of Psychiatry 1994;151:628-29. <P>31. Nakagawa Y. Death with dignity in Japanese culture. Psychiatry and Clinical Neurosciences,      1995;49(Suppl 1):S161-63.<HR>
