<HTML>

<HEAD>

<TITLE>Welcome to King & Spalding</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<body bgcolor="ffffff" body text="#000000" body link="#00009c" body vlink="#8e2323">

<P>

<center>

<a href="/gif/ksart5.map"><img src="/gif/ksart5.gif" ismap></a>

</center>

<CENTER><H4><a href="/menu/groups.htm">[Practice Groups]</a>

<a href="/menu/attorn.htm">[Attorneys]</a>

<a href="/menu/articles.htm">[Articles]</a>

<a href="/menu/leglink.htm">[Legal Resources]</a>

<A HREF="/menu/recruit.htm">[Recruiting]</A>

<A HREF="/menu/contact.htm">[Locations]</A>

</H4>

</center>

<P>

<hr>

<p>

</center>

<P>

The law firm of <FONT SIZE=+1>K</FONT>ing &amp; <FONT SIZE=+1>S</FONT>palding was founded in Atlanta, Georgia in 1885 and has over 340 lawyers.<p>

<p>

The Firm maintains a broad-based general legal practice that is both national and international in scope. It represents some of America's best known companies and acts as counsel to corporations, government agencies and individuals in Western and Eastern Europe, the Middle East, the Far East, Mexico and Latin America.<p>



<FONT SIZE=+1>K</FONT>ing &amp; <FONT SIZE=+1>S</FONT>palding has offices in Atlanta, GA, Washington, DC, New York, NY and Houston, TX. Lawyers include a former Attorney General of the United States, a former Governor of the State of Georgia, and numerous other lawyers who have held high-level positions in the federal government.<p>



If you would like to obtain additional information about <FONT SIZE=+1>K</FONT>ing & <FONT SIZE=+1>S</FONT>palding, please contact <A HREF="http:/menu/ads.htm">Adair Dorsey Sisk, Director of Client Services</A>. For additional information about this World Wide Web site, please contact <A HREF="http:/menu/brad.htm">Bradley A. Slutsky, Esq.</A>

<P><HR>

<small>

Please read our <A HREF="http:/disclaim.htm">Copyright and Disclaimer page</A>.  In addition, pursuant to Florida Bar Rule 4-7.2(d), we need to inform you on our home page that the hiring of a lawyer is an important decision that should not be based solely upon advertisements.  Before you decide, ask us to send you free written information about our qualifications and experience.  Pursuant to State Bar of Texas Rule 7.04(j), we also need to identify a principal office on our home page, and we designate our office in Atlanta, Georgia for that purpose.<P>

</small><P>

</BODY>

</HTML>





