Bob Bryant is a partner in King & Spalding's Corporate Practice Group. He joined the Firm in 1978 and practices in the Atlanta office.
<P>
Mr. Bryant has experience in a wide variety of corporate transactions,
including mergers, acquisitions and joint ventures.
<P>
